    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“《Sanatorium: A Mental Asylum Simulator》是我见过最独特的游戏之一” - VICE</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是“咆哮的二十年代”，一个技术进步和社会剧变的时代。随着你周围的城市不断扩张，你感到自己被落下了：一个疲惫的记者，背负着债务，漫无目的。然后，一个儿时朋友突然发来一条神秘信息——也许是一生中最大的线索。它指向了臭名昭著的 Castle Woods 疗养院。那里有一个谜团在等着你，你无法抑制揭开它的冲动。这也许只是一个直觉，但感觉这像是一个可以改变一切的秘密。甚至是你自己。你下定了决心：你收拾行囊，出发前往 Castle Woods。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059090/extras/0e8d373fd5e2d917f25a0b8c7430cf84.avif?t=1762468571\" width=617 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >考验你的智慧和直觉。每周，新的病历都会带来新的谜题亟待解决，你要决定使用哪些测试来发现症状，以及开出哪些治疗方案来治愈他们。是决定遵循规则手册，还是尝试结果未知的实验性新疗法？你是想仁慈还是残酷？是精于算计还是勇于冒险？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开 Castle Woods 洁净外表背后隐藏的黑暗秘密。邂逅无助的病人、冷酷的机会主义者以及一系列其他有趣的角色。收集线索，拼凑出关于疗养院和你自己过去的惊人真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059090/extras/5a851942e624b2dc5ec493560757ae2e.poster.avif?t=1762468571\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059090/extras/5a851942e624b2dc5ec493560757ae2e.webm?t=1762468571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059090/extras/5a851942e624b2dc5ec493560757ae2e.mp4?t=1762468571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059090/extras/24fe95c900d6d387d7c4fca0952e891c.avif?t=1762468571\" width=617 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059090/extras/f5132bb8b3b4882b50ed75c04c9fb259.poster.avif?t=1762468571\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059090/extras/f5132bb8b3b4882b50ed75c04c9fb259.webm?t=1762468571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059090/extras/f5132bb8b3b4882b50ed75c04c9fb259.mp4?t=1762468571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>卡牌驱动的职场模拟</strong> — 扮演 1923 年的医生，每一个行动都受到那个时代过时的工具和信念的束缚。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>诊断、“治疗”或保留</strong> — 决定是遵循严酷、陈旧的方法，还是怀着同情心行事，同时深知两种选择都会带来后果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每位病人都是一个谜题</strong> — 病历如分层的卡牌组般展开，症状在有限的知识中被隐藏、揭示和误解。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>横跨 4 个章节的完整战役</strong> — 揭开 Castle Woods 的秘密，以及被困在其高墙内的生命。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>分支路径，多种结局</strong> — 你的决定不仅塑造了病人的结局，也决定了你作为冒名顶替者的命运。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超过 100 张卡牌可供记录</strong> — 症状、疾病、测试和治疗方法均源于精神病学动荡不安的历史。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>改进你的治疗方案</strong> — 将治疗方案升级为更人道的做法，或者加倍使用那些不惜一切代价保护你身份的方法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059090/extras/974134021d6102b9755cd5b318033cb6.poster.avif?t=1762468571\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059090/extras/974134021d6102b9755cd5b318033cb6.webm?t=1762468571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059090/extras/974134021d6102b9755cd5b318033cb6.mp4?t=1762468571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059090/extras/96fd26ae68f9e73d451ec7e2e2e66c02.avif?t=1762468571\" width=617 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入我们的 Discord，并在我们的平台上关注我们，以获取更新、阅读我们的每周开发日记，并成为社区的一员！</p>",
